SUMMARY:Children’s Bingo
DTSTAMP:20260625T094518Z
DTSTART:20260625T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Bring the kiddos and join our Levy Park team for Children’s Bin
	go! This 30-minute program\, ideal for kids aged 4 to 12\, is a fun way fo
	r children to practice their letters and numbers while earning prizes. Lev
	y Park provides Bingo cards\, markers\, and prizes. B-I-N-G-O!\n\nhttps://
	www.levyparkhouston.org/events/childrens-bingo/2026-06-25/\n\nFrom Levy Pa
	rk Houston
