SUMMARY:Blue Dragon Tai Chi
DTSTAMP:20260625T094518Z
DTSTART:20260625T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Levy Park with Taoist Healing for Tai Chi and Medita
	tion every Friday at 9 AM and every Thursday 6 PM. Practice Tai Chi to con
	nect and focus the body and mind with slow\, low-impact gentle movements a
	nd stretches. Open to all ages and levels\, this class is great for those 
	who want to de-stress\, find their inner peace\, and increase overall heal
	th.\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/blue-dragon-tai-chi-2-3/2026
	-06-25/\n\nFrom Levy Park Houston
